UralChem Agrees on $400 Million Eight-Year Loan From Sberbank

-- B y   I l y a   K h r e n n i k o v
-- 
2011-10-03T07:09:04Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-03/uralchem-agrees-on-400-million-eight-year-loan-from-sberbank.html
UralChem, a Russian fertilizer maker,
agreed on a $400 million, eight-year loan from state-run OAO
Sberbank to help repay debt, according to a regulatory filing
today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Ilya Khrennikov in Moscow at 
